<L>__{interior world of donuts day}
<A>__{evening. henry enters and sits with bunuel.}
<C>__{bunuel}
<D>__{how are you, henry?}
<C>__{henry}
<P>__{(frowning)}
<D>__{peachy. gimme a light.}
<C>__{bunuel}
<D>__{have you found a job?}
<A>__{henry just glares at him and smokes.}
<C>__{bunuel}
<D>__{how 'bout those alcoholics anonymous meetings, did you go over and visit them yet?}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{what happened to this assistant librarian position you were supposed to set me up with?}
<A>__{bunuel looks down, disappointed.}
<C>__{bunuel}
<D>__{i tried, henry. i really did.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{so what happened?}
