<D>__{henry, with your background... well, i mean, with your record, they didn't think it'd be right to have you at the neighborhood library.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{why not?}
<C>__{bunuel}
<D>__{they thought you'd be a bad influence on the kids.}
<A>__{henry sits back, offended.}
